{"tid":1751083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葉劉: 泛民拉出政治議題「非常政治化」","createTime":"2019-11-24T15:47:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T17:13:26.000Z","uid":42188,"like":29,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"819d3e168648b67bbbb5b3a4ed3ecc8e7aff0bf5","tid":1751083,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:47:35.000Z","msg":"新民黨主席葉劉淑儀在投票結束後再到海怡西票站外。她說因今日奔走多個選區，加上對陳家珮充滿信心，故最後才到海怡西為陳拉票。<span style=\"color: red;\">她說投票率高是意料中事，泛民拉出政治議題，「係非常政治化」</span>，但相信多區輸贏差距很小。"},{"pid":"5db395ac32c769463f54a81e1275a2a9cdaeeca4","tid":1751083,"uid":258696,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:48:05.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咪撚做休息撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n投完票，贏輸都好，我地有新野做。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">文宣方向：</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 有得一人一票，社會氣氛好左幾多？而且大家都相信投票，年青人到長者教出黎投，所以應該一人一票選特首。<br />\n<br />\n2.我地要將種票、票多過投票人、送禮各種唔公平現象比英美兩國知。<br />\n<br />\n3. Poly手足被困多日，要求警察撤退。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBe water be humble </span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"39f8009577f2be20479366011991edb0ae5da1fd","tid":1751083,"uid":19552,"like":74,"dislike":0,"score":74,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:48:36.000Z","msg":"屌你老母保皇黨講政治化講上腦 選舉唔係政治唔通係性愛呀"},{"pid":"3c01e90c9e0bdb73a497bab75c584e1af31254f6","tid":1751083,"uid":18547,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:48:45.000Z","msg":"投票都唔應該政治化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face